{"tid":2436943,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"全孝盛瘦身不瘦胸 大騷36D豐滿上圍誘fans","createTime":"2021-03-07T13:45:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T14:34:48.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dc15620bceab5c18c0f6bd6171b9c7f40791b595","tid":2436943,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T13:45:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/GdOcIA4Nw5W8h3Q8zxwAdZ4Em9Y=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FGTA4525NFBUZPWADBCOLUL23Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FGdOcIA4Nw5W8h3Q8zxwAdZ4Em9Y%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFGTA4525NFBUZPWADBCOLUL23Y.jpg&h=501704a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓國女團Secret出身的31歲女星全孝盛擁有36D逼爆上圍，就算近年她積極瘦身，但仍然瘦身不瘦胸，令不少女網民及fans大呼羨慕，她亦有在個人YouTube頻道公開減肥心得，靠不同運動減到只有101.2磅（46KG），認真有恆心。而全孝盛昨日在IG公開新相，她打開外面的皮質外套，內裏穿着黑色吊帶背心，大方騷豐滿上圍誘fans，至於另一張相就見她隱約露出美腿，纖瘦身形十分好看。<br />\n<br />\n申才恩黑絲誘惑<br />\n另外，同樣愛作性感打扮的人妻模特兒申才恩，昨日亦在IG上載自己穿上爆乳泳裝的照片，而她今日就外出嘆美食，雖然打扮較密實，但她就穿上短褲配黑絲的造型，大晒長腿。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jCkWT_MUCJ90ClZNlIaLEPvZLJ8=/802x1002/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3M2KF4QROZCDDLKBBFBME25U5E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjCkWT_MUCJ90ClZNlIaLEPvZLJ8%3D%2F802x1002%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3M2KF4QROZCDDLKBBFBME25U5E.jpg&h=f4b1e0c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uVWAh_XGyF5dnYCF1RMQNfvMFP0=/802x1159/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EGRRYNRCH5F55D4OBELUOL2W3Q.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FuVWAh_XGyF5dnYCF1RMQNfvMFP0%3D%2F802x1159%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEGRRYNRCH5F55D4OBELUOL2W3Q.JPG&h=9bbc41f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/GoNQSqUePTPfJNMODN_LIIZUHx0=/802x814/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NJ3SCDZ6XBH6VFY7UX3XVKAGDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FGoNQSqUePTPfJNMODN_LIIZUHx0%3D%2F802x814%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNJ3SCDZ6XBH6VFY7UX3XVKAGDM.jpg&h=98f51882&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jq79pTla_ch3xmDBNKiRplvdfdg=/802x1081/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/43EWEY3KOFFXPHT7BTPLQGZNIY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fjq79pTla_ch3xmDBNKiRplvdfdg%3D%2F802x1081%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F43EWEY3KOFFXPHT7BTPLQGZNIY.jpg&h=a70a0115&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ajJvxdPuZqT5ZzeNJzJsvWdbC1Q=/802x997/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AK5VSC3RAZGEBMWHPPIQWHZXDE.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FajJvxdPuZqT5ZzeNJzJsvWdbC1Q%3D%2F802x997%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAK5VSC3RAZGEBMWHPPIQWHZXDE.JPG&h=e3bfd8d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3PyW_8fxevdi31QLuwOCSI8BmI8=/802x933/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NQL3HO24RNFMPOD6A2OWTDCU44.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3PyW_8fxevdi31QLuwOCSI8BmI8%3D%2F802x933%2Ffilters%3Aq